Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, you get nervous\Nwhen you have to do something{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for the first time too, don't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thinking you have to do it right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've just landed my first leading role.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I practiced lots and did my best,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I still got scolded for some reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I just don't get it \Nat all. I don't. I don't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yaritai koto wa nani {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sou kikareru tabi {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aoi sora miageta {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kotae wa only my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honto ni daiji na kotoba\Nwa kantan ni wa iwanai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikari ga yubisasu\Nbasho e to hashiridasu yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakishimetai mono nara\Nnakitai hodo mune ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egakitsuzukete yuku kitto take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiroi kumo ga nagareru\Nchiheisen no mukou ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:02:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naranderu mirai wa itsumo soba ni aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sora Naegino, who is\Nplaying the role of the Little Mermaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Anna Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Kenneth Presentation is\Na special two week performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you will enjoy the fresh new cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you excited to play the lead role?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something to Miss Layla,\Nwho is shooting a movie right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, there's a photo shoot\Nfor posters and a newspaper interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the day after tomorrow,\Na photo shoot for pamphlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, an appearance on cable TV has been set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, it just doesn't feel real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, you're the leading lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leading lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Facing an Amazing Wall."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to snap out of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The photo shoot for the\Nposter has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Mermaid, let's\Nlook a little more vibrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, get a little\Ncloser to the Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you set a more romantic mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna really looked handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me feel really shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know. You guys look very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally... how should I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I wanted it to be more like a jellyfish\N waiting for his lover...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sure it'll be a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hope so, for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in it, it would,\Nlike, be an absolute success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get to you, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won the part through pure talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla used to play the Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? What? Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a special presentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've been given the\Nleading role for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your mom happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but she was worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first leading role,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can easily see you pushing too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to play the same\Nrole that Miss Layla played,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I have no choice but to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ken, did you bring that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Miss Layla's Little Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see this one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, my performance\Nwill just be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm also looking forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--to seeing your Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla's Little Mermaid is\Nas wonderful as I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so gorgeous and graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience is so moved and crying so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's famous for being\Na show that makes people cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage's Little Mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could perform like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem awfully giddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but can you afford such an attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reverse Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card means that if\Nyou keep being indecisive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will lose everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like it if you would look at\Nme just as passionately once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said opening day is sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried nobody would\Nshow up because it's not Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Sora looks wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredibly graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you're the best! The best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Sora really great?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was a perfect performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Sora coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Sarah went\Nthrough all this trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to celebrate her hugely\Nsuccessful opening day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate Sora's share too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always in the\Nmood to celebrate anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I want to touch the\Naudience's hearts and make them cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience is getting smaller\Ncompared to opening day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't made any\Nparticularly big mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think the show itself has\Nbeen perfected to a high degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kenneth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it would have been\Nbetter to reopen the show with Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I may not be as good as Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm working hard to reach her level of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to understand\Nwhy I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos, summon Layla back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's still in the\Nmiddle of shooting the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then have her replace Sora as\Nthe lead as soon as she's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Mr. Kenneth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the way it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, are those the questionnaires\Nup through yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It was a new cast, but it was wonderful,\Njust like watching Miss Layla."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The stage was very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this is the birth of\Nthe next generation's Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would like to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla's Little Mermaid \Nwith the new set."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's written anything negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's all about Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think your Little Mermaid is bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't move people either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that because I'm imitating\NMiss Layla's performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I played the Little Mermaid\Nthat Miss Layla created perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are not Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep being indecisive,\Nyou will lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what he meant when he said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for two Miss Laylas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, the show's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't appear\Non stage feeling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:11:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I should perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, the show can't start without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go{\i0}! You're the leading lady, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was unusually harsh, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wall every new lead comes up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have to really agonize\Nover it and I'm sure it'll be hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if she can't overcome that wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she won't ever be able\Nto make a role her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't know. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was such a mess today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience will not\Nbuy that kind of excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience didn't come all this\Nway to see a half-baked performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the person playing\Nopposite you, I will say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to perform seriously tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's think about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About {\i1}your {\i0}Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Little Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to understand\Nwhy I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it a performance\Nthat they've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That they've never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Anna, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone watches the show as\Nif they were the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't understand the character,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way the character's\Nfeelings will get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what Sora's\NLittle Mermaid would be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you'll have to get a grasp\Non the Little Mermaid's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mermaid's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm supposed to be a mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sora is working at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is about\Nthe only thing I can do for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Oh" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to be\Nso laid back and goofing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But being a mermaid is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very beautiful in the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you get to swim around it all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no intensive training either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nobody who's\Nmean to you or yells at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a girl who grew up like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would probably be a cheerful,\Nspirited, and genuine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Little Mermaid is\Nsupposed to be a tragic heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she should be a girl like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking isn't going to get me anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm just going to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen the\NLittle Mermaid make people laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she finally lost her mind\Nfrom the pressure of being the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, what did you\Nthink of today's Little Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to get your honest opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was kind of an\Nenergetic and cute Little Mermaid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't tie in with the part when\Nshe turned into bubbles at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess it felt a little incoherent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think if it were Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would have been a\Nmore graceful and refined Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you thinking,\Nasking the audience questions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't know unless I ask them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll only get more confused\Nif I just think on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a bit of an improvement, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Little Mermaid was\Ndifferent from Miss Layla's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose your personality\Nis showing through more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also prefer the way you are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with your performance today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever heard of a Little Mermaid like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It becomes a problem for us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you suddenly decide\Nto change your performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you never got permission\Nfrom the production department!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to play a different\NLittle Mermaid than Miss Layla's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This show is only two weeks long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please don't confuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, we got carried away too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ended up throwing the\Nproduction into confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not your fault. I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not wrong, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that no one\Nunderstands your Little Mermaid yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The run of the show has just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you perfect a performance\Nthat can convince everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "only two weeks."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two {\i1}whole {\i0}weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than doing it halfway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the plunge and\Ncreate my very own Little Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to live like the\NLittle Mermaid during the production.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't produce a calculated\Nperformance like she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to find\Nmy role with my own mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, don't you think you're going too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feet are probably numb\Nfrom wearing fins all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been swimming all her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she suddenly grew legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the Little Mermaid might trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought a lot about the\NLittle Mermaid's feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Little Mermaid\Nloves the prince, and that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she went so far as to exchange\Nher voice to become a human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though the prince\Nthinks the wrong person saved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she doesn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really something she can't help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think there might be other ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were her, I couldn't give up\Nsomeone I seriously loved that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how could she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's get everyone else's opinions too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the Little Mermaid\Nhave to give up her love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being unable to express\Nourselves through words
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is something we have to\Ndeal with on stage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can still express\Nourselves by using our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never thought about\Nanything outside of the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, for a modern-day audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Little Mermaid who quietly\Nwithdraws herself might not be satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what if she tries really hard to tell\Nhim that she was the one who saved him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll even duel the princess\Nfrom the neighboring kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, the prince\Nstill doesn't remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what would the Little Mermaid do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the prince's hand and\Njump into the water together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, the prince will\Nalso jump into the waterfall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them will fall down\Nthe waterfall, holding each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that fall, the prince will\Nremember the Little Mermaid and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid has a\Nstrong tragic image, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I like happy\Nendings better than tragedies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like this might\Nturn into an interesting show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we get Kalos's permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take the plunge to change the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished the film shoot early,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since Mr. Kenneth contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First she completely\Nimitates my performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now she's come up with\Nan outrageous Little Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess playing the lead role\Nwas still too much for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have a look at it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this kind of attendance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no wonder Mr. Kenneth is complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid is testing the sea witch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see if the sea witch can really use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the sea witch could be a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just absurd...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, just watch\Nit through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blue ribbon represents waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying to make the prince remember her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Little Mermaid like that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted was a\Nnew kind of Kaleido Star
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we'd never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that Little Mermaid cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized the Little\NMermaid was such a fun story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I was able to\Nreally enjoy performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I've got a little idea\Nfor the ballroom scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should transform\Nthe starfish into tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Little Mermaid is\Ndefinitely Sora's own creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's become the leading\Nperformer and the troupe leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an amazing girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Sora's Little Mermaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the supporting cast were lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they were given\Nunconventional new characters to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we have a new\Ntitle added to Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Little Mermaid that paves her own way.
